        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Charitable Donation Relief Act of 2005 - Waives limitations under the Internal Revenue Code on income tax deductions for individual and corporate charitable contributions made after August 28, 2005, and before January 1, 2006, for the relief of victims of Hurricane Katrina.</p>]]></text>
